OL,7,FA footballer says he "wouldn't be here
OL,8,Ftoday" without his wife, who performed
OL,9,Flife-saving CPR after he had a cardiac
OL,10,Farrest in his sleep three years ago.
OL,12,FAdam Dodd's wife Kat learned CPR
OL,13,Fthrough her job as a teacher, and
OL,14,Fafter waking up to him gasping for air
OL,15,Fand unresponsive, she performed CPR
OL,16,Fwhich saved his life.
