OL,3,CFootballer 'wouldn't be here today'
OL,4,Cwithout his wife who did life-saving
OL,5,CCPR
OL,7,FKat said: "I remember thinking in my
OL,8,Fhead 'please don't die please don't
OL,9,Fdie like I can't lose you.' I kept
OL,10,Fthinking you are my life, like we have
OL,11,Fa life together, this is not
OL,12,Fhappening."
OL,14,F"It was actually really really
OL,15,Ftraumatic and it has taken us quite a
OL,16,Fbit of time for both of us to get over
OL,17,Fthe mental effects of the trauma that
OL,18,Fit's had but obviously we're here and
OL,19,Fwe've had a great outcome."
