OL,5,CCPR
OL,7,FAdam, who is now back playing football
OL,8,Ffor Bamber Bridge FC, spent five days
OL,9,Fin an induced coma before he was
OL,10,Ffitted with an implantable
OL,11,Fcardioverter defibrillator which
OL,12,Fprotects him from life threatening
OL,13,Fheart rhythms.
OL,15,FHe said: "Within three minutes you are
OL,16,Fdead if no one gets to you to do CPR
OL,17,Fso that's how much of a phenomenal job
OL,18,Fshe did, otherwise I wouldn't be there
OL,19,Ftoday."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
