OL,5,CCPR
OL,7,FThe couple are both backing the
OL,8,FBritish Heart Foundation's Every
OL,9,FMinute Matters Campaign.
OL,11,FKat said: "We want people to just take
OL,12,F15 minutes of their time over
OL,13,FChristmas maybe when they are with
OL,14,Ftheir family and go onto the British
OL,15,FHeart Foundation website and learn CPR
OL,16,F- it takes 15 minutes of your time.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
