OL,7,F"It's a really easy video to follow
OL,8,Fand then you never know you might need
OL,9,Fit. I never thought I would need it
OL,10,Fand it saved my husband's life so for
OL,11,F15 minutes of your time it's really
OL,12,Fworth doing."
OL,14,FLizzie Moscardini from the British
OL,15,FHeart Foundation said: "It's really
OL,16,Fimportant in a cardiac arrest
OL,17,Fsituation that people act really fast
OL,18,Fbecause every minute really does
OL,19,Fmatter.
