OL,7,F"Of those out-of-hospital cardiac
OL,8,Farrests, 80% of those do happen in the
OL,9,Fhome, so you are more likely to have
OL,10,Fto use those skills on a loved one, so
OL,11,Fit's really important that everyone
OL,12,Fknows what to do in that situation."
